article_title: The Evil Genius Of Obamacare's Millennial Mandate

article_metadata.description: ObamaCare’s Millennial mandate may be the perfect crime. Politicians hand out benefits, but no one can tell who’s paying.
article_metadata.author: Michael F. Cannon
